with Temp_Queue() as temp_Queue:
    queue = temp_Queue.queue
    queue.push({'var_1': 'value_1', 'var_2': 'value_2'})
    assert queue.get_message() == '{"var_1": "value_1", "var_2": "value_2"}'
    queue.push({'var_3': 'value_3', 'var_4': 'value_4'})
    assert queue.pull() == {'var_3': 'value_3', 'var_4': 'value_4'}
    queue.push([{'var_5': 'value_5'}, {'var_6': 'value_7'}])
    assert queue.pull() == [{'var_5': 'value_5'}, {'var_6': 'value_7'}]
